ture that unites independent brands under a single roof, is supported by technology, and based on sustainable growth. We don't just produce services — we create markets, build systems, and share profits.","card_1_title":"Ecosystem Management","card_1_desc":"We manage all our brands under a single, integrated structure.","card_2_title":"Digital Infrastructure","card_2_desc":"We control processes end-to-end with our own software and operational systems.","card_3_title":"Local Development","card_3_desc":"We offer a fair model that centers around tradesmen, producers, and entrepreneurs.","corporate_structure":"Corporate Structure","quote":"Our goal is not just to build a marketplace, but to construct a fully integrated economic system extending from producer to consumer.","quote_author":"Chairman of the Board"},"brands":{"badge":"Our Ecosystem","title_main":"Growing Strong","title_highlight":"Together","description":"Every brand within Hızır Global acts with a common infrastructure and vision. This structure ensures sustainable success across different sectors.","yetis_carsi":{"desc":"A marketplace platform that integrates local tradesmen into the digital economy and strengthens local commerce."},"yetis_yemek":{"desc":"A new generation food ecosystem that brings together restaurants, couriers, and customers in a single system."},"yetis_edepo":{"desc":"End-to-end logistics, stock, and distribution infrastructure for producers and sellers."},"hizir":{"desc":"The ecosystem's power on the field: a fast, controlled, and integrated distribution network."},"yte":{"desc":"Technology-based transportation solutions for national and international commerce."}},"ecosystem":{"title_main":"Start Your Own Business,","title_highlight":"Join a Huge System","description":"The Hızır Global ecosystem offers entrepreneurs not just a brand, but infrastructure, customers, technology, and operational support. You are not alone here. You are part of a system."},"footer":{"description":"We are bu